N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 448.6 - Shore signs regulating navigation

State Regulations

All signs placed on shore which shall prohibit, zone, control or regulate navigation shall display the same color, symbol and
lettering in good proportion as required on special marker buoys of the same
significance. Notes
